{"tid":1300981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"抵制賣港賊合味道","createTime":"2019-07-09T13:46:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T13:46:05.000Z","uid":85736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8fabcd86caa39e0045717ff69b99174d796ac1c0","tid":1300981,"uid":85736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T13:46:05.000Z","msg":"香港市面合味道：中国製<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中国、台灣、歐洲等地合味道：香港製<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/熱爆話題/57221/香港出售合味道非港產-日清證僅剩兩口味於香港製造\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C%2F57221%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%87%BA%E5%94%AE%E5%90%88%E5%91%B3%E9%81%93%E9%9D%9E%E6%B8%AF%E7%94%A2-%E6%97%A5%E6%B8%85%E8%AD%89%E5%83%85%E5%89%A9%E5%85%A9%E5%8F%A3%E5%91%B3%E6%96%BC%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%A3%BD%E9%80%A0&d=xVNj5QJXHW0KkW%2Bw8ZKC7PDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=30dfa1cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/熱爆話題/57221/香港出售合味道非港產-日清證僅剩兩口味於香港製造</a>（30/11/2016）<br />\n<br />\n&quot;日清 ... 為顧及原料及產品穩定供應 ... 將合味道杯麵轉移到順德工場進行生產，亦因同樣原因，「咖喱海鮮味」及「牛奶海鮮味」則繼續在香港生產。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;記者 ... 發現咖喱海鮮味75克普通版確為香港製造，但增量版大杯麵「Big Cup」咖喱海鮮味卻是中國製造。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;至於不少網民在內地、台灣及東南亞等地發現香港製造的合味道杯麵，日清指「由於出口至台灣的合味道數量不多，所以會繼續由香港負責生產」。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n一星期前攝於荷蘭（殘體字、香港製）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8BhKw6G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8BhKw6G.jpg&h=a131a2aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩日前攝於香港759（正體字、中国製）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3vdxFZ2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3vdxFZ2.jpg&h=449d7a20&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}